  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SquareButton
    The SquareButton class is a simple SWT widget that can be used in place of a native SWT button.
    SquareButton.DefaultButtonClickHandler
    Use this instead of using an explicit mouse adapter, unless you have other reason to.
    SquareButton.SquareButtonBuilder
    Not totally necessary, but it's lovely to chain a bunch of calls together for efficiency and brevity of code.
    SquareButton.SquareButtonColorGroup  
    SquareButtonGroup
    Currently this is primarily used for square buttons used like a toggle.
